thread.title_full: Disc Makers reviewed by Charlie Finn

author: Charlie Finn
title: Charlie Finn
text: We r very happy with the CDs made and with the quality and color of the print work on the paper cover of the jewel case. The only thing missing was that the case was not taped closed to give the impression that the cd was pristine new and has not been opened. Minor point. Again, pretty happy overall with the product.
